Package: dsDashboard
Type: Package
Title: Dashboard Framework for DataSHIELD Applications
Version: 0.4.0
Author: Andreas Mändle
Maintainer: Andreas Mändle <maendle@leibniz-bips.de>
Description: Provides a framework for building interactive dashboards in R.
    The package is designed to support data analysis both on local data and
    on data on a DataSHIELD server.
